For Chemical, Biological, Radiological, and Nuclear, Biological, (CBRN) Survivability, only Chemical, Biological, and Radiological contamination survivability is required. Nuclear survivability is not required. Two types of Cargo Sleds will be developed to accommodate the dimensions of the supported aircraft: a small Cargo Sled designed for use with MV-22 and a large Cargo Sled developed for use with CH-53k and C-130 aircraft. 

Cargo Sled Requirements 

