12. DD Form 2345 - ITAR/EAR Certification: For proposals whose solutions fall under export- controlled regulations (either International Traffic in Arms (ITAR) or Export Administration Regulations (EAR)), a copy of the certified DD Form 2345, Militarily Critical Technical Data Agreement, or evidence of application submission must be included. The form, instructions, and FAQs may be found at the United States/Canada Joint Certification Program website, https://www.dla.mil/LogisticsOperations/Services/JCP/. Approval of the DD Form 2345 will be verified if proposal is chosen for award. 

